description: Look no further! From the popular scratch sleeves and tubular wraps maker, Edenswear, here is the newest selection of socks to help those affected by eczema and dry skin on their feet. The unique fiber blend of TENCEL and SMARTCEL SENSITIVE makes the socks most suitable for eczema and other skin irritations. Wearing these socks will allow the skin to heal without uncontrollable scratching causing further damage. ✌️✌️Edenswear Zinc-Infused Socks are layered with TENCEL and SMARTCEL SENSITIVE to provide the thickness and the softness to prevent damages to the skin from excessive scratching and rubbing. Benefits of TENCEL and SMARTCEL SENSITIVE: TENCEL is a natural fiber that’s growing in popularity because of its many beneficial properties, such as having the softness of cotton, the breathability of linen, the smoothness of silk, and the natural properties of wool. Zinc is infused with TENCEL in a special blending process to create a patented material called SMARTCEL SENSITIVE. Zinc has proven clinically effective in reducing flares, and soothe irritations. Zinc oxide is found in many anti-itch creams for eczema and other skin conditions.
